Martin,

If it is less than $5K, then get it... don't worry about the engine.  A
rust-free double cab, especially one that old, is an impossible find.  Heck,
$6K would be low.  These things are RARE, most were used and abused.  A 40
year old pick-up truck and the bed is in "excellent shape"!

I'm sure someone can help you on the engine questions... I just wanted to
chime in that you have a one-of-a-kind find.

  Stephen Gutknecht
  Renton, Washington
  1963 Double Cab
  1967 Westy


